parameters.name: Quality_wi_3dp
parameters.description: Q, Quality parameter for electron data. It is calculated from the properties of the input data and goodness-of-fit statistics from the nonlinear fitting process.  It varies between 0 and 10. Higher values of Q represent more confidence in the resulting electron parameters
